Forth Ports May Get Formal Bid From Arcus This Week, Times Says

-- B y   D a v i d   A l t a n e r
-- 
2011-03-20T09:05:28Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-20/forth-ports-may-get-formal-bid-from-arcus-this-week-times-says.html
  Forth Ports Plc (FPT)  may get a formal
744 million-pound ($1.2 billion) bid this week from its biggest
shareholder, Arcus Capital, the Sunday Times said, citing an
identified person.  Management will probably recommend the offer to
stockholders, the newspaper said. Arcus owns 22.8 percent of the
U.K. ports operator, the Times said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
David Altaner in London at 
 daltaner@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Colin Keatinge in London at 
 Ckeatinge@bloomberg.net  